	   <tr><td colspan=2>depending on the status of the group, or raid that your involved in a wiz may be asked to debuff a mob, snare a mob, or nuke a mob .. those are really the main reasons to have a wiz.. now people very much overlook what a wiz is best for its not just nuking..its AE nuking.. wiz is capable of taking down multiple targets at a time.. you need to understand more about this and only real way is to be a wiz.. and get to lvl 50+ where it is utilized more.. plus u need to have a group that understands this as well.. honestly in my opinion ive tried almost every class .. wiz has been the hardest .. not because its boring.. i think its a blast being a wiz.. my fav char.. but its a challenge to find your place in the group and raid situations.. like i said.. it really depends on the situation.. other notables for wizzies..is obviously easy movement.. including luclin now.. and being able to say make a lil cash on the side using those ports and tl's<br>as far as soloing.. wiz is a root and nuke tatic soloer until you learn to kite.. which happens usually for most people around 34.. using bonds of force to snare mobs at a time..and circle of force as your first true &quot;quad&quot; kiting spell.. or four mobs at a time.. <br>anyway.. i am very happy to be a wiz in the game.. i have alts.. quite a few.. most mellee but the wiz has been the most fun in the game thus far.. good luck to you!<br>taygarr<br>wiz of the 55th season<br>the seventh hammer<br>&nbsp;<br>WIZROG!!!!!!!!</td></tr>
